titocc.compiler.types

Class ArrayType

  • java.lang.Object
    • titocc.compiler.types.CType
      • titocc.compiler.types.ArrayType

  • public class ArrayType
extends CType
    Corresponds to C array type. Is an object, but not scalar or arithmetic. Equals only to ArrayType that has same element type and length.
